courses.subject: Support Elective
courses.customDesc:
Any Support Elective course can go here.

Select one from the following: CD424; ES320, ES321, ES322, ES323, ES380, ES381; ES/WGQS350; PSY260, PSY304; PSY/WGQS324; WGQS301, WGQS320, WGQS340; WGQS/RELS370. Some courses on this list may have prerequisites that may be taken as Free Electives. If GE courses are taken for a letter grade and used as Support Elective, additional Free Elective units may be required to complete the 180 total degree requirement. See college advisor for additional information.
